                            <comment id="14477546" author="paulk" created="Thu, 11 Oct 2007 07:48:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Now has the ability to run like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java -cp %GROOVY_CLASSPATH% org.codehaus.groovy.tools.xml.DomToGroovy infile.xml &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;outfile.groovy&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

